                                            the
                                            delay.</li>
                                        <li>When you reach the destination, click the <b>Arrived</b> button to notify
                                            the
                                            completion of the trip.</li>
                                        <li>If needed, you can click the <b>Stop</b> button to pause or end the driving
                                            session.
                                        </li>
